{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"06793701a5718d02b84eb8b7843e5449","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete picture of the current state:\n- Portal already exists with PWA, i18n, 5 core packages, Supabase, OpenAI, Three.js\n- 5 core packages already implemented: astrology, cabala, iching, odus, tantra\n- Has i18n (`/locale` directory)\n- Has Onboarding, Ritual, Dashboard, Mandala components\n- Uses Next.js 16.2.6\n- Has Stripe, Supabase, web-push already wired\n- Has pdf generation (@react-pdf/renderer, jspdf)\n\nThe \"4 Pilares\" mention in manifest.json is OUTDATED (should be 5 after R-011). I'll note this in the UX doc as a future fix.\n\nNow I have all the context to write a comprehensive ux/architecture_v1.md. Let me structure it:\n\n**Sections:**\n1. TL;DR — Decisão UX (PWA + Mandala + Mandato + Mural + Mentor)\n2. Princípios de design (8, derivados de patterns.md)\n3. Personas & jornadas\n4. Decisão Mobile-first: PWA vs App Nativo (justifica PWA)\n5. Estrutura de descoberta progressiva (micro-doses)\n6. Telas-chave (5 telas: Mandala/Mandato/Mural/Ritual/Mentor)\n7. Interação com IA (streaming/voz/texto)\n8. Acessibilidade WCAG 2.2 AA\n9. Internacionalização (PT-BR first, EN depois)\n10. Stack técnico mínimo (PWA + Web Push + Service Worker)\n11. Validação com 3 perfis (Ana/Bruno/Carla expandido)\n12. Métricas de UX\n13. Anti-padrões rejeitados\n14. Bibliografia\n15. Próximos passos (D-005, D-022 detalhamento)\n\nLet me write it. Target: ~600-800 lines.","signature":"6950fd10b8feef8df0e6a2a3507caf47e55e1f312366896ef4c6b25b47356cfe"}],"model":"MiniMax-M3","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard"},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"061a3f19-d22b-419e-8188-4f359ca6b060","uuid":"ec795308-c3bd-4d25-9a71-b399ef9cb356"}
